            "name": "Social Timeline",
            "description": "Social media feed with post creation and interaction buttons",
            "content": "<!-- Social timeline container -->\n<div class=\"container\" role=\"main\">\n  <h1 id=\"timeline-heading\">Social feed</h1>\n\n  <!-- Post creation form -->\n  <section class=\"post-composer\" aria-labelledby=\"composer-heading\">\n    <h2 id=\"composer-heading\" class=\"sr-only\">Create new post</h2>\n    <form class=\"composer-form\" aria-label=\"Create a new post\">\n      <img \n        src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/48\" \n        alt=\"Your profile picture\" \n        class=\"composer-avatar\">\n      <div class=\"composer-content\">\n        <label for=\"post-text\" class=\"sr-only\">What's on your mind?</label>\n        <textarea \n          id=\"post-text\" \n          name=\"post-text\" \n          rows=\"3\" \n          placeholder=\"What's on your mind?\"\n          aria-label=\"Post content\"></textarea>\n        <div class=\"composer-actions\">\n          <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn-icon\" aria-label=\"Add photo\">\n            <span aria-hidden=\"true\">üì∑</span> Photo\n          </button>\n          <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn-icon\" aria-label=\"Add video\">\n            <span aria-hidden=\"true\">üé•</span> Video\n          </button>\n          <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn-icon\" aria-label=\"Add emoji\">\n            <span aria-hidden=\"true\">üòä</span> Emoji\n          </button>\n          <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn\" aria-label=\"Publish post\">Post</button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </form>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- Social posts timeline -->\n  <div class=\"timeline\" role=\"feed\" aria-labelledby=\"timeline-heading\">\n    <!-- Post 1 -->\n    <article class=\"post\" role=\"article\" aria-labelledby=\"post-1-author\">\n      <header class=\"post-header\">\n        <img \n          src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/48\" \n          alt=\"Profile picture of Sarah Johnson\" \n          class=\"post-avatar\">\n        <div class=\"post-meta\">\n          <h3 id=\"post-1-author\" class=\"post-author\">Sarah Johnson</h3>\n          <time datetime=\"2025-11-28T14:30:00\" class=\"post-time\">2 hours ago</time>\n        </div>\n        <button class=\"btn-icon post-menu\" aria-label=\"Post options\">\n          <span aria-hidden=\"true\">‚ãÆ</span>\n        </button>\n      </header>\n      <div class=\"post-content\">\n        <p>Just launched our new product dashboard! Really excited about the features we've built. Check it out and let me know what you think! üöÄ</p>\n        <img \n          src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/600x400\" \n          alt=\"Screenshot of new product dashboard\" \n          class=\"post-image\">\n      </div>\n      <footer class=\"post-footer\">\n        <div class=\"post-stats\" aria-label=\"Post engagement statistics\">\n          <span>24 likes</span>\n          <span>8 comments</span>\n          <span>3 shares</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"post-actions\">\n          <button class=\"post-action\" aria-label=\"Like this post\" aria-pressed=\"false\">\n            <span aria-hidden=\"true\">üëç</span> Like\n          </button>\n          <button class=\"post-action\" aria-label=\"Comment on this post\">\n            <span aria-hidden=\"true\">üí¨</span> Comment\n          </button>\n          <button class=\"post-action\" aria-label=\"Share this post\">\n            <span aria-hidden=\"true\">‚ÜóÔ∏è</span> Share\n          </button>\n        </div>\n      </footer>\n    </article>\n\n    <!-- Post 2 -->\n    <article class=\"post\" role=\"article\" aria-labelledby=\"post-2-author\">\n      <header class=\"post-header\">\n        <img \n          src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/48\" \n          alt=\"Profile picture of Michael Chen\" \n          class=\"post-avatar\">\n        <div class=\"post-meta\">\n          <h3 id=\"post-2-author\" class=\"post-author\">Michael Chen</h3>\n          <time datetime=\"2025-11-28T11:15:00\" class=\"post-time\">5 hours ago</time>\n        </div>\n        <button class=\"btn-icon post-menu\" aria-label=\"Post options\">\n          <span aria-hidden=\"true\">‚ãÆ</span>\n        </button>\n      </header>\n      <div class=\"post-content\">\n        <p>Great team meeting today! Proud of what we accomplished this quarter. Here's to an even better next quarter! üí™</p>\n      </div>\n      <footer class=\"post-footer\">\n        <div class=\"post-stats\" aria-label=\"Post engagement statistics\">\n          <span>42 likes</span>\n          <span>12 comments</span>\n          <span>5 shares</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"post-actions\">\n          <button class=\"post-action\" aria-label=\"Like this post\" aria-pressed=\"false\">\n            <span aria-hidden=\"true\">üëç</span> Like\n          </button>\n          <button class=\"post-action\" aria-label=\"Comment on this post\">\n            <span aria-hidden=\"true\">üí¨</span> Comment\n          </button>\n          <button class=\"post-action\" aria-label=\"Share this post\">\n            <span aria-hidden=\"true\">‚ÜóÔ∏è</span> Share\n          </button>\n        </div>\n      </footer>\n    </article>\n\n    <!-- Post 3 -->\n    <article class=\"post\" role=\"article\" aria-labelledby=\"post-3-author\">\n      <header class=\"post-header\">\n        <img \n          src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/48\" \n          alt=\"Profile picture of Emily Rodriguez\" \n          class=\"post-avatar\">\n        <div class=\"post-meta\">\n          <h3 id=\"post-3-author\" class=\"post-author\">Emily Rodriguez</h3>\n          <time datetime=\"2025-11-27T16:45:00\" class=\"post-time\">Yesterday at 4:45 PM</time>\n        </div>\n        <button class=\"btn-icon post-menu\" aria-label=\"Post options\">\n          <span aria-hidden=\"true\">‚ãÆ</span>\n        </button>\n      </header>\n      <div class=\"post-content\">\n        <p>Anyone else working on interesting projects this week? Would love to hear what you're building! Drop a comment below üëá</p>\n      </div>\n      <footer class=\"post-footer\">\n        <div class=\"post-stats\" aria-label=\"Post engagement statistics\">\n          <span>18 likes</span>\n          <span>23 comments</span>\n          <span>2 shares</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"post-actions\">\n          <button class=\"post-action\" aria-label=\"Like this post\" aria-pressed=\"true\">\n            <span aria-hidden=\"true\">üëç</span> Like\n          </button>\n          <button class=\"post-action\" aria-label=\"Comment on this post\">\n            <span aria-hidden=\"true\">üí¨</span> Comment\n          </button>\n          <button class=\"post-action\" aria-label=\"Share this post\">\n            <span aria-hidden=\"true\">‚ÜóÔ∏è</span> Share\n          </button>\n        </div>\n      </footer>\n    </article>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- Visually hidden class for screen readers -->\n<style>\n.sr-only {\n  position: absolute;\n  width: 1px;\n  height: 1px;\n  padding: 0;\n  margin: -1px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);\n  white-space: nowrap;\n  border-width: 0;\n}\n</style>"
